thread.title: Ana Cristina Diaz
thread.title_full: KatchAKid reviewed by Ana Cristina Diaz

author: Ana Cristina Diaz
title: Ana Cristina Diaz
text:
We just got our new katchakid net installed and the entire process and service were Great! Mike & Lavandis came to installed the net and they left everything clean the installation process was quicker than what I expected. They called me ahead of time to let me know they were on the way and their explanation was very clear and they took heir time to make sure we understood how to put it in and out.
Definetly getting peace of mind with this net. Good warranty. I will recommend them 100%.
